            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-12">
            <div class="do-box">
              <%= image_tag("team.png") %>
              <h3>精英团队</h3>
              <p>找到理想的工作，最靠谱的老板，高格调的团队，百万年薪不是梦 。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-12">
            <div class="do-box">
              <%= image_tag("serendipity.png") %>
              <h3>Serendipity</h3>
              <p>赚到人生第一桶金，邂逅幸运女神，开启财富自由之门。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<!-- /.the third section(service advantage) -->

<!-- the forth section(hot title) -->
<section id="genius" class="our-experts">
